Name: Archon Elmer
Description: With alien technology this destructive defender finally finds that wascally wabbit and the Earth within his grasp.

Name: Astronaut Hector
Description: A strong attacker able to tear down enemies who are taunting and remove their positive effects!

Name: Astronaut Sylvester
Description: Turns out a cat in 0G is an excellent tank able to dodge and steal his enemies positive effects!

Name: Barber Bugs
Description: Awesome support. Focuses on keeping his team alive by constantly healing them and clearing negative effects.

Name: Barkeep Sheepdog
Description: Keep the peace with cocktails that heal allies to full or slow enemies rousing when enemies crit.

Name: Barnyard Dawg
Description: Sneaky attacker. Able to hide away from danger and unleash a strong attack on the enemies.

Name: Baseball Bugs
Description: Left fielder right fielder centerfielder outfielder shortstop pitcher and catcher all at once this Critical Attacker keeps the bases loaded.

Name: Bat-Suit Wile
Description: It's not the flight suit Wile needs but the one he deserves.

Name: Bellboy Daffy
Description: This staff duck serves his Defender allies offering amenities like Speed Up Attack Up and heals.

Name: Bellboy Gossamer
Description: This staff monster serves his Attacker allies offering amenities like Defense Up Turn Meter and Taunt.

Name: Black Knight Sam
Description: The Black Knight is able to use his dragon to inflict heavy Damage Over Time on his enemies.

Name: Bugs Bunny
Description: A versatile damage dealer with an AoE selective Stun and burst of sustain. Loves his buddy Porky Pig.

Name: Bugs the Brave
Description: This heroic paladin throws himself in front of enemy attacks becoming immune to damage when his team needs him.

Name: Cannoneer Canasta
Description: Anyone who attempts to Counter this hulking defender is getting dragged into the briny deep.

Name: Captain Bligh
Description: Look at you! Consorting with Outlaws? Receiving Stat Downs? Disgrace to the Navy! Avast there you lazy layabouts!

Name: Chamberlain Porky
Description: A versatile Support serving up heals Debuff removal and dynamite-stuffed poultry.

Name: Chauffeur Porky
Description: The fastest chauffeur in the city able to speed up his allies and give them an edge in battle.

Name: Chef Porky
Description: This hearty cook boosts his team's Max Health and heals proportionally.

Name: Climber Granny
Description: A geriatric athlete with limited but relentless abilities. She's fitter than you and knows it.

Name: Contender Sylvester
Description: This Defender comes out strong healing with each hit he takes and when Southpaw connects.

Name: Cowboy Bugs
Description: Western attacker. The cowboy is excellent when fighting with desert toons.

Name: Cowboy Sylvester
Description: Evasive defender. Protects his team by drawing attention to himself and rolling away from danger.

Name: Cowgirl Granny
Description: Support cowgirl. Helps her team by providing a lot of critical chance and counter attack chance.

Name: Cupid Elmer
Description: A hunter of hearts who leaves enemies weak-kneed and cleanses all of the past's pain.

Name: Curator Porky
Description: An aggressive utility-Support who both cleanses and inflicts Stun offering Counter Chance Up.

Name: Daffy Duck
Description: A critical hit-based scoundrel who sharpens the bills of other Daffies and ignores enemy Defense. Truly dethspicable.

Name: Daffy Hood
Description: Robbing the rich and giving it to himself Daffy Hood excels at finishing off weakened enemies and speeding up his allies.

Name: Desperado Dawg
Description: An infamous outlaw who hides his teammates for the perfect ambush.

Name: Devil Dog
Description: Too hot to Freeze Hector's devilish side Debuffs entire enemy teams and annihilates Heal Over Time.

Name: Don Henery
Description: The capo dei capi is here to bring some order to his house of Outlaws. Keep the Don safe there'll be something in it for you.

Name: Dr. Dawgstein
Description: Great supporter. Excellent at giving critical hits to his team and healing his allies in danger.

Name: Duck Dodgers
Description: A powerful attacker who can reduce the cooldown of his special skill to deal massive amounts of damage!

Name: Egghead Jr.
Description: This little polymath has a plan to protect his team from Crits and Flip anything that comes his way.

Name: Egghead the Knowing
Description: Both apprentice and master a young magician who learns all that which should remain unknown.

Name: Elf Daffy Duck
Description: A supporter duck who can turn bad effects into good.

Name: Elmer Fudd
Description: A hunter who pwotects his Forest friends keeping critical hitters in check.

Name: Elmer the Sure
Description: A selfish knight who becomes stronger the more he's protected.

Name: Farmer Hector
Description: Stout defender. Good against high defense defenders and cats.

Name: Farmer Petunia
Description: This attacker is capable of dealing damage while protecting her allies with amazing defense boosts and healing abilities!

Name: Farmer Porky
Description: Support farmer. Helps his team by healing them and weakening the enemies.

Name: Fishercat Sylvester Jr.
Description: A chipper little healer fishing for victories by buffing his team's Attack. He loves when allies gain Hidden!

Name: Flamenco Prissy
Description: This fiery dancer Dodges through enemy advances and keeps her peers moving.

Name: Foghorn Leghorn
Description: Strong defender. Protects his team from enemies especially when team members are low on health.

Name: Foghorn the Invincible
Description: A walking fortress who wants all the armor for himself.

Name: Friar Porky
Description: This laughing tank protects his team by greatly slowing down his enemies.

Name: Gossamer
Description: This scary tank specializes in greatly slowing down his enemies and ignoring his target's defense.

Name: Grand Duke Sylvester
Description: The Grand Duke is able to sniff out hidden enemies and attack them with righteous fury.

Name: Granny
Description: A senior healer able to empower her allies and weaken her enemies.

Name: Gridiron Gossamer
Description: A beefy linebacker with his eyes on the prize. Once he builds momentum good game!

Name: Handmaiden Granny
Description: This healing assistant is an expert at Healing Over Time and cleansing her allies.

Name: Hector
Description: This very resistant tank steps into the front lines to defend his team and reveal hidden enemies.

Name: Henery Hawk
Description: All appetite and no patience this chicken hawk chomps through Max Health with Lifesteal against chickens.

Name: Henery Hike
Description: This receiver may be small but there's no stopping him once he's got some Speed Up under his wings.

Name: Hippety Hopper
Description: With Legendary strength this boxer side-steps counters and dodge to smash non-Defender enemies with Haymakers.

Name: Holiday Bugs Bunny
Description: A defender with a special knack for helping out allies and stunning opponents.

Name: Hugo
Description: The Abominable Snow-Man is out searching for pet of his own and freezing everything in his path.

Name: Hunter Yosemite Sam
Description: A cantankerous critical hitter with counter chance and a hatred of rabbits.

Name: Huntsman Porky
Description: This axeman cuts through Defenders while sheltering your own. Good luck staying warm with this hunter in the snow.

Name: Jester Bugs
Description: Only a fool would strike this prankster and his allies.

Name: Joe Monday
Description: This gumshoe duck cracks cases and skulls alike with guaranteed crits constant Counter Chance and immunity from all Debuffs.

Name: K'Chutha Sa'am
Description: A powerful tank who's able to lifesteal while taunting and deal large amounts of damage to his enemies.

Name: K-9
Description: Marvin's loyal second-in-commander ready to sniff out and mark targets and their planets for total annihilation.

Name: King Bugs Bunny
Description: The king rules at stunning his enemies and inflicting them with taunt.

Name: King Daffy
Description: More monarch than mallard this greedy attacker can't go a turn without Stealing a Buff.

Name: Kitty Ketty
Description: A master of Assist this kitty commands the battlefield through her allies healing in urgent waves.

Name: Leopold
Description: The maestro can protect his team and deal large amounts of damage with his gran finale.

Name: Lola
Description: An irrepressible bunny babe with zero chill. Nothing this cute should do this much damage.

Name: Lola Frostbane
Description: A mysterious marauder from the distant north who emboldens those who can face the Chill.

Name: Lunar Petunia
Description: A force of peace in a world of mayhem. When the moon rises so does her power.

Name: Mail Runner
Description: Nothing stops this mailman - not even Taunt - from delivering damage.

Name: Martian Bugs
Description: A rabbit with an invisibility device that allows him to hide from enemy and counter attack if attacked!

Name: Marvin
Description: The martian who started it all is armed to the teeth with powerful weapons.

Name: Marvin Fudd
Description: The brightest laser in the woods melting single targets from above Whenever an enemy falls his Trigger Finger pulls.

Name: Masked Avenger
Description: Awesome avenger. The Masked Avenger brings justice straight to his enemies' health attacking quickly and decisively.

Name: Master Speedy
Description: This wushu master slows and dodges enemies keeping his hero allies on the righteous path.

Name: Matador Bugs
Description: This crowd-pleaser baits enemies into his Taunt with timely Silences dodging to roaring applause.

Name: Merlin Sam
Description: The wizard greatly slows down his enemies and inflicts them with Damage Over Time.

Name: Miss Prissy
Description: High damage critical hits. Unpredictable chick can land a critical on all attacks.

Name: Monster Foghorn
Description: Lifestealer defender. Steals a lot of health from his target and jumps in front of danger to save his allies.

Name: Monster Tweety
Description: A sip of Hyde Juice turned Tweety into a Debuffing Countering menace who fears no Taunt.

Name: Mountain Man Sam
Description: A cranky hermit alone for a reason. Try to cool his temper and you'll get burned.

Name: Mountie Elmer
Description: A resilient tundra trooper at home in the cold who keeps his team clear of debuffs.

Name: Mr. Bugs
Description: This tragic hero lives for his Supports Assisting and boosting Defense when times are dark.

Name: Mr. Sam
Description: A stout scam artist able to protect his team and heal himself.

Name: Nasty Canasta
Description: This brute smashes foes with multi-hits and Damage Over Time strengthening with each kill.

Name: Ninja Ralph
Description: A skirting shadow. A bird in flight. A stealthy shinobi who will not let honor get in the way of his prize.

Name: O'Pat
Description: The mischievous chief of the leprechauns will Steal and Scramble to protect his precious pot o' gold.

Name: Officer Prissy
Description: A sharp-eyed Cop who leaves the Outlaws seeing red.

Name: Officer Yosemite
Description: Powerful support. Deals lots of damage and buffs his allies.

Name: Outback Dawg
Description: This hunter offers teamwide Counter Chance archetype-based Debuffs and a handy self-heal/cleanse.

Name: Outlaw Foghorn
Description: Counterattack specialist. The Mystery Man can counter attacks and stop his enemies from countering also.

Name: Outlaw Sylvester
Description: Critical supporter. Able to raise critical hits for all his team and hit taunting enemies.

Name: Penelope
Description: Pursuit made this Attacker an expert at dodging - especially when afflicted with Damage Over Time. What's Taunt to a cat on the run?

Name: Penelope Couture
Description: Too haute for her enemies this sophisti-cat and her cohorts dodge advances while empowering artists.

Name: Pepe Le Bard
Description: The bard uses his songs to heavily boost and heal his allies in battle.

Name: Pepe Le Pew
Description: The persistent odiferous Attacker leaves his mark with Damage Over Time. When Penelope attacks his heart races.

Name: Petunia Pig
Description: A crafty healer with a strong personality and an even stronger right hook.

Name: Phantom Le Pew
Description: From the shadows this monster fixates on a single enemy drawing strength from their sorrow.

Name: Photographer Sylvester
Description: An artist whose camera slows enemies. With work this Stunning it's no wonder he Hides from the public.

Name: Picador Sylvester Jr.
Description: Every Matador needs a Picador to Silence enemies inflict DoTs and remove enemy Stat Ups.

Name: Police Dog Hector
Description: Defensive police dog. Able to soak in a lot of damage and protect his allies while also helping them get ahead in the battle.

Name: Porky Pig
Description: Balanced support swine. This friendly swine can heal his allies and dish out some damage to his enemies.

Name: Prizefighter Daffy
Description: This featherweight Defender gains Taunt with his enemies arming Daffy teams to the bill.

Name: Professor Prissy
Description: Nothing slows this explorer down and her Speed-related buffs keep her whole team at pace.

Name: Queso Bandito
Description: This little Mouse can do fast attacks and help your team. You'll only hear the breeze when he comes to steal your cheese!

Name: Raider Lola
Description: This explorer showers enemies with debuffs via crit-capable AoEs revealing all that's Hidden.

Name: Ralph the Vampire
Description: Fast attacker. The vampire is able to sustain himself in battle while he deals large amounts of damage to his enemies.

Name: Ralph Wolf
Description: High risk attacker. Uses his multipurpose kit to set up strong attacks.

Name: Referee Foghorn
Description: An arbitrator who calls all the shots. Stick to his rules or he'll have you sitting this one out.

Name: Reindeer Road Runner
Description: Once every year this magical supporter travels the world Silencing all in his wake.

Name: Revenant Road Runner
Description: Here he comes to steal your soul - and deliver Crits!

Name: Road Runner
Description: Fast support. Avoids enemy damage while debuffing his enemies and speeding up his team.

Name: Rocket Coyote
Description: Risky but very damaging attacker who thrives against Damage Over Time.

Name: Rocket Sylvester
Description: A special support character who truly shines when accompanied by coyotes.

Name: Ronin Canasta
Description: A wandering swordsman with no home or master who poisons everything of value to him.

Name: Royal Page Coyote
Description: A volatile servant of the king he's able to inflict Damage Over Time on several enemies at once.

Name: Salesduck Daffy
Description: Multipurpose duck. This persistent duck can eat through taunt enemies with his guaranteed criticals.

Name: Sam Sheepdog
Description: Big and slow but vigilant and ready with a counter for enemies eying his flock.

Name: Samurai Sheepdog
Description: Loyal guardian to the Shrine. This defender stands his ground and grows stronger from his enemies' hesitation.

Name: Scarecrow Sylvester
Description: Debilitating expert. Defeats his enemies by greatly weakening them and doing health based damage.

Name: Scarlet Pumpernickel
Description: The Scarlet Pumpernickel is a master swordsman who can hide from his foes and attack them with impunity.

Name: Scout Foghorn
Description: A beefy scout who Taunts and Stuns enemies buffing his buddy Scout Sylvester.

Name: Scout Leader Granny
Description: A caring scout who keeps her allies on their feet buffing the Max Health of woodland critters.

Name: Scout Sylvester
Description: A sneaky scout who attacks from Hidden buffing his buddy Scout Foghorn.

Name: Scrooge Yosemite Sam
Description: An attacker who also helps his team with high risk reward effects.

Name: Sea Goin' Sam
Description: This irate pirate is out looking for Bounties. With his crew of Outlaws around there's no escaping him.

Name: Settler Granny
Description: Support settler. Able to heal her allies and cleanse their wounds.

Name: Sheriff Porky
Description: Support peacekeeper. The sheriff protects his allies by weakening their enemies and quickly jumping into action.

Name: Show Biz Bugs
Description: This rabbit debuffs enemies and saves his allies from a bad performance!

Name: Show Biz Daffy
Description: This duck thrives from stunning his enemies with his team's performance!

Name: Siegfried Elmer
Description: Calling thunder he's able to dish out heavy damage to all foes while standing in the front lines protecting his team.

Name: Space Cadet
Description: A support toon able to give his allies lots of defense and heal his tanks!

Name: Space Explorer Granny
Description: Granny's invisibility cloak allows her to speed up her allies actions giving them an edge on the battle!

Name: Speedskater Coyote
Description: Race this coyote at your own risk. His competition Freezes faster than the rink.

Name: Speedy Gonzales
Description: ¡Andale! With AoE Ignore Dodge and extra attacks on random targets good luck avoiding this mouse.

Name: Star-Pharaoh Marvin
Description: The One True Healer comes from beyond the cosmos to Debuff false idols.

Name: Starseeker Lola
Description: This deepspace explorer debuffs Hidden enemies dodging or countering attacks.

Name: Super-Rabbit
Description: A timed woodland creature turned into the superdynamic rabbit of tomorrow.

Name: Sylvester
Description: This sneaky cat can easily become hidden and lash out large amounts of damages on his enemies.

Name: Sylvester Jr.
Description: This kitty follows allies into Hiding and heals the team when they emerge popping out to Stun.

Name: Sylvester Slaszlo
Description: This rebel on the run Assists from safety scaling damage with each Defense Up on his team.

Name: Sylvester the Brash
Description: A speedy cavalier who takes advantage of Defense Down to deliver devastating Critical hits.

Name: Tasmanian She-Devil
Description: This surly defender Flips debuffs on her team and steals Turn Meter for tempo. Pair with Taz for max effect.

Name: Taz
Description: This whirlwind Scrambles and Flips enemy buffs enraging at low Health. Pair with She-Devil for mayhem.

Name: The Flaming Succotash
Description: A misfire of science had transformed a mild-mannered kitty into a luminary beacon of justice. This flaming feline now roams the city skies with an obligation to cook the crooks.

Name: Tourist Daffy
Description: Daffy took a right turn at Albuquerque and now needs to Cleanse Buff and call on Rabbit allies to Assist if he wants to survive.

Name: Trapper Sylvester
Description: A sneaky hunter exploiting the cold to nab his prey. If you can't see him he probably sees you.

Name: Treasure Hunter Tweety
Description: A healer and finisher all in one this bird smashes foes with boulders from the safety of its team.

Name: Tweety
Description: The cutest little bird you ever did taw. Why lift a feather when your allies do the work?

Name: Tweety the Twue
Description: A knight banneret who keeps his team well-stocked in both defense and offense.

Name: Valkyrie Bugs
Description: A support valkyrie who can greatly expedite her team's actions and silence her enemies.

Name: Van Wile
Description: A well-equipped Monster hunter with nerves of steel and bullets of silver.

Name: Waiter Elmer
Description: The waiter supports his team by healing and empowering his allies especially good when fighting rabbits.

Name: Western Type Hero
Description: Critical striker. Dealing high amounts of damage through his critical skills he's able to quickly defeat his foes.

Name: Wildcard Wolf
Description: Collect Buffs deal crits and Stun or Silence enemies who call this gambler out.

Name: Wile E. Coyote
Description: This must-answer mastermind brings tricks to stifle yours a self-healing appetite for birds and an ever-climbing Attack stat.

Name: Winter Bugs
Description: With unavoidable Chilly and overwhelming Critical effects this attacker brings the Summit to his enemies.

Name: Witch Hazel
Description: The wicked witch uses Damage Over Time to defeat those who attack her dealing heavy damage.

Name: Witch Lezah
Description: The witch supports her team by being hidden and stealing her enemies positive effects!

Name: Witchdoctor Hazel
Description: In the darkest jungle this Taunting witch inflicts DoTs Silence all enemies and buffs the Attack of magic allies.

Name: Yeti Gossamer
Description: The blizzard itself bringing the cold to the whole fight. Enemies Freeze while allies thaw just enough.

Name: Yodel Le Pew
Description: This yodeler wears his enemies down with terrible singing turning their strengths against them while shrugging off their critiques.

Name: Yokai Taz
Description: This spirit of destruction has been summoned from realms beyond to empower Monsters with Critical Damage.

Name: Yosemite Sam
Description: Selfish attacker. Deals high damage to enemies and removes attack bonuses from all characters.

Name: Zoot Suit Daffy
Description: How different it was in my native village... Dodge Chance Flip the enemy team in Silence their buffs removed... And then there was Stun...
